title: 15 min Calisthenics Workout | No Equipment | All Levels
description:
Check out this 15 min full body Calisthenics workout which will prepare you for skills like the human flag, planche, any lever etc. The exercises target specifically the muscle groups engaged in these Calisthenics skills.

The best is that you can do this workout at home and without any equipment! No bars, no parallettes needed. The only thing you need is yourself and motivation.

Give your best - 40 sec full energy!

channelDescription:

• FITNESS: Focus on own-bodyweight training, particulary 𝐂𝐀𝐋𝐈𝐒𝐓𝐇𝐄𝐍𝐈𝐂𝐒 & 𝐁𝐁𝐎𝐘𝐈𝐍𝐆 (𝐁𝐑𝐄𝐀𝐊𝐃𝐀𝐍𝐂𝐄) are my specialties.
